							Hail members... and welcome visitors!If you havent' heard by now, I've been elected the newest officer and leader of "House 4" of the Crimson Dragons.  The way I see it, "House 4" has gone nameless for long enough.  We need an identity!  That's why I'm calling on all Crimson Dragon members to head over to the OOC board in the tavern and post what you think would be a good name for the fourth house of the guild.  You can see my message scribbled there for more details.Hail members... and welcome visitors!If you havent' heard by now, I've been elected the newest officer and leader of "House 4" of the Crimson Dragons.  The way I see it, "House 4" has gone nameless for long enough.  We need an identity!  That's why I'm calling on all Crimson Dragon members to head over to the OOC board in the tavern and post what you think would be a good name for the fourth house of the guild.  You can see my message scribbled there for more details.
							<br>~ <a href="mailto:rahsalynd@raveworld.net">Rahsalynd</a><br><br>
